{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDAwODQ4MDE1", "number": 16864, "title": "Add public API to load configuration files", "bodyText": "Add load() method to Config, ClientConfig, and ClientFailoverConfig. This method loads the config with the \"known\" locations. If not found, the default config is returned.\nfix #16809\nRelated to spring-projects/spring-boot#19487\nThis is the completion of the initial work done by @jerrinot and opened as a draft PR: #16386, I addressed all the comments from there.", "createdAt": "2020-04-08T13:27:23Z", "url": "https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast/pull/16864", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "9c7c62f0eec24219c60fd8f92a9e8c52695fba6e"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-04-17T09:13:35Z", "author": {"login": "leszko"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 15, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABb2EvN5AH2gAyNDAwODQ4MDE1Ojk2NjllOTI5ZmE1NzQ3Yzg1ZDBiN2M3ODdhNDVlZWQ0YjUxNDAzNjY=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABcYceTFAH2gAyNDAwODQ4MDE1OmU2MzIwMmNmZTIxMzA3NzI3NWFlNTQzYjZkZmIxYmFmMzA1NzBmNTY=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "9669e929fa5747c85d0b7c787a45eed4b5140366", "author": {"user": {"login": "jerrinot", "name": "Jaromir Hamala"}}, "url": "https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast/commit/9669e929fa5747c85d0b7c787a45eed4b5140366", "committedDate": "2020-01-01T12:58:02Z", "message": "Factory to populate Config object from well-known locations\n\nIt allows to load config from an external file and then customize\nit programmatically. This is useful when embedding Hazelcast into\nmanaged environments: When a runtime container wants to create an\ninstance as if it was created via `Hazelcast.newHazelcastInstance()`,\nbut it wants to inject an instance of `ManagedContext` into Hazelcast\nconfiguration.\n\nWithout this capability all containers have to duplicate the `Config`\nlocation strategy: \"First try this, then that, etc.\"\n\nRelated to https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-boot/issues/19487\n\nTODO: Tests"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "045fa0f584d9a02c4ff145f91a716ec27b30514b", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast/commit/045fa0f584d9a02c4ff145f91a716ec27b30514b", "committedDate": "2020-04-07T12:32:58Z", "message": "Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast into experiments/populate-config-from-default"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "7e87221aba0bb4f1c0783cc58dc4bb292d9501de", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast/commit/7e87221aba0bb4f1c0783cc58dc4bb292d9501de", "committedDate": "2020-04-07T15:19:21Z", "message": "Fix after code review"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "30f2748676dce15cb19c582da6067e76325c6112", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast/commit/30f2748676dce15cb19c582da6067e76325c6112", "committedDate": "2020-04-07T15:47:49Z", "message": "Add ClientConfig.load()"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "079e4dd900a8df959b9913c275892635596db23a", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast/commit/079e4dd900a8df959b9913c275892635596db23a", "committedDate": "2020-04-07T15:50:05Z", "message": "Fix FailoverConfigTest"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "eb27d3a3aebe819b074575abc1c5b1fe692b0f59", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast/commit/eb27d3a3aebe819b074575abc1c5b1fe692b0f59", "committedDate": "2020-04-08T11:26:02Z", "message": "Add unit tests"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "53ac17632e6f6911827caf094e3363ed13e2c3ac", "author": {"user": null}, "url": "https://github.com/hazelcast/hazelcast/commit/53ac17632e6f6911827caf094e3363ed13e2c3ac", "committedDate": "2020-04-08T12:39:33Z", "message": "Add ClientFailoverConfig.load() and